===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|weven|t=to weave|id=to weave}}, from {{inh|en|ang|wefan||to weave}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*weban}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*webaną}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*webʰ-||to weave, braid}}. 

